    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "25. He addresses \"the daughter of Zion\" (Jer 6:23); caution to the citizens of Jerusalem not to expose themselves to the enemy by going outside of the city walls.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "sword of the enemy—literally, \"there is a sword to the enemy\"; the enemy hath a sword.",
        "children": []
